Package com.github.rolecraftdev.guild

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Guild
    Represents a Guild in Rolecraft.
    GuildListener
    Listens for and manipulates various events depending on the guild config
    GuildManager
    Stores Guild data and Guild-related configuration options and manages Guilds in Rolecraft.
    GuildRank
    Represents a player rank within a specific Guild.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GuildAction
    A representation of all of the GuildActions which can be performed and are related to Guilds in one way or another.
